139cfdd89204e0/87945/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/b95e4/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/1779b/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/87945/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/5a523/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/b95e4/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 256w,\n/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/1779b/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 512w,\n/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/87945/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 1024w,\n/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/5a523/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg 1200w\" src=\"/static/e9eea904ed9d002733139cfdd89204e0/87945/De-Gris-a-POSITHIVO-07-04-2019.00_05_22_16.Still007-1-1200x675-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></figure></li></ul></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>&#8220;De Gris a POSITHIVO&#8221; Documental Autobiográfico de Juan De La Mar que hace parte de Luv &#8217;til it Hurts, se encuentra seleccionado para “Media Library 2020 &#8211; Visions Du Réel, Festival Internacional de Cine de Nyon”.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>&#8220;De Gris a POSITHIVO,&#8221; an Autobiographical Documentary by Juan De La Mar, who is part of Luv &#8217;til it Hurts, has been selected for the “Media Library 2020 &#8211; Visions Du Réel, Festival Internacional de Cine de Nyon.”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Además, con este documental hemos sido seleccionadxs en festivales de cine LGBT como “CinHomo”, “Andalesgai”, “El Lugar Sin Límites”, “Yukasa”; y nos ha permitido hablar en diferentes contextos sobre el VIH.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>In addition, with this documentary we have also been selected to LGBT film festivals, such as “CinHomo,” “Andalesgai,” “El Lugar Sin Límites,” “Yukasa;”</em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Los invitamos a ver y compartir este tráiler y a preguntarse ¿qué harían si mañana fuera su último día de VIHda?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>We invite you to watch and share this trailer, and to ask yourself: what would you do tomorrow if it was the last day of your life (VIHda)?</em></p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Trailer documental &quot;De gris a posithivo&quot;. Director Juan de la Mar.\" width=\"580\" height=\"326\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/JCIR7dt24hg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Para saber más sobre el proyecto:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>To learn more about the project:<br></em><br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.salmonproducciones.com/asesorias-y-alianzas/de-gris-a-posithivo.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.salmonproducciones.com/asesorias-y-alianzas/de-gris-a-posithivo.html</a><br><br><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.visionsdureel.ch/2020/media-film/de-gris-a-posithivo?fbclid=IwAR3JvAgpTERt_9ixbdHgteldt4OgfhPyCmYsEUCMs9vz5KAIj41spRIDcIM\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.visionsdureel.ch/2020/media-film/de-gris-a-posithivo?fbclid=IwAR3JvAgpTERt_9ixbdHgteldt4OgfhPyCmYsEUCMs9vz5KAIj41spRIDcIM</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Contacto: </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Contact:</em> </p>\n\n\n\n<p>posithivoequipo@gmail.com</p>\n","link":"/what-would-you-do-tomorrow-if-it-was-the-last-day-of-your-life-vihda/","author":{"node":{"name":"Juan De La Mar"}},"featuredImage":null,"categories":{"nodes":[{"slug":"hummingbird","ACFCategoryData":{"color":"#3d358b","colorHigh":"#f35b04","pageicon":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/a1266245dab422a6fe54272d16c0046b/hummingbird-page.png"}}}}]},"tags":{"nodes":[{"slug":"spaceship","ACFTagData":{"tagimage":{"localFile":{"publicURL":"/static/806e71b8eec6911d6bdbd17736bdc1cc/spaceship-tag.png"}}}}]}},"nextPage":{"title":"#movingtarget","uri":"/movingtarget/"},"previousPage":{"title":"Please, touch me (PT/EN)","uri":"/please-touch-me-pt-en/"}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDozNjI1","nextPage":"cG9zdDoyNzM1","previousPage":"cG9zdDoyOTA5"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2005293003"]}